NFStest provides a set of tools for testing either 
the NFS client or the NFS server, included tests focused mainly 
on testing the client.

nfstest_cache - Valid for any version of NFS
nfstest_delegation - Valid for any version of NFS granting delegations
nfstest_dio - Valid for NFSv4.0 and NFSv4.1 including pNFS
nfstest_pnfs - Only valid using NFSv4.1 with pNFS enabled and file layout type
nfstest_posix -	Valid for any version of NFS
